We are the chosen generation, 𝐚 𝐠𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐟 𝐕𝐢𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐤𝐞𝐫𝐬, we talk our way Up and out of anything contrary to our faith, because our mouth is our weapon and we are fully geared with the word of God.\
We don’t fight for #victory, we fight from #victory, the good fight of faith because the #prophecy went ahead, thus, we can’t die! Isaiah 33:24 ” AND THEY THAT DWELL / LIVE IN ZION / CHRIST SHALL NOT SAY, I AM SICK;”…. we have THE VICTORY OVER Covid_19.
